&lt;p&gt;Are you ready to transform the way businesses pay and get paid? Bottomline is a global leader in business payments and cash management, with over 35 years of experience and moving more than $16 trillion in payments annually. We&#39;re looking for passionate individuals to join our team and help drive impactful results for our customers. If you&#39;re dedicated to delighting customers and promoting growth and innovation - we want you on our team!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;The Role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
