&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Senior Data &amp;amp; Financial Analyst&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to help innovate, win, and grow with us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; This is a &lt;strong&gt;hybrid role based in Portsmouth, NH&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
